00:00:57,458 --> 00:01:00,500
- ♪ YEAH, YEAH, YEAH ♪
- ♪ YEAH, YEAH, YEAH ♪

9
00:01:00,583 --> 00:01:03,750
- ♪ THE ROCK CITY BOY ♪
- ♪ THE ROCK CITY BOY ♪

