00:01:03,833 --> 00:01:05,125
- ♪ OH, BABY,
YEAH, YEAH ♪

11
00:01:05,208 --> 00:01:06,916
( singing in Japanese )

12
00:01:28,208 --> 00:01:31,125
♪ MY PERFECT DREAM! ♪

13
00:01:38,041 --> 00:01:40,000
- Chorus: ♪ YEAH, YEAH, YEAH ♪

14
00:01:40,083 --> 00:01:42,166
♪ THE ROCK CITY BOY ♪

15
00:01:42,250 --> 00:01:43,291
♪ BOY, BOY, BOY ♪

16
00:01:43,375 --> 00:01:45,791
( singing in Japanese )

17
00:01:49,166 --> 00:01:50,791
- ♪ I WANNA BELIEVE
THE SING ON THE BEAT ♪

18
00:01:50,875 --> 00:01:52,458
♪ MOST RECENTLY
